# generated code — *_templ.go ARE committed so `git pull` + `go build` deploys
# pick up template changes without running `templ generate` on the host.
# Regenerate with `make gen`; never hand-edit. Only the auxiliary text tables
# (not needed to build) stay ignored.
*_templ.txt

